/p>\n<p>In order to map Laniakea, the astronomers looked at thousands of galaxies to calculate where they are going and how quickly. Laniakea's boundaries depend on those calculations, and since the Milky Way and the earth are near the edge, it is possible that a different mathematical approach would place us in <a href=\"http:\/\/www.thedailybeast.com\/articles\/2014\/09\/07\/laniakea-the-milky-way-s-place-in-the-heavens.html\">a different supercluster<\/a>. Whether that supercluster would then be Laniakea or something else entirely is an open question.<\/p>\n","author":"Max Ehrenfreund","date":"September 9 at 10:11 am","link":"http:\/\/knowmore.washingtonpost.com\/2014\/09\/09\/the-vast-cosmic-structure-containing-the-milky-way-has-been-named-laniakea\/","format":"video","info":{"fs_type":"video","fs_uuid":null,"fs_url":"http:\/\/www.washingtonpost.com\/news\/speaking-of-science\/wp\/2014\/09\/03\/for-the-first-time-our-region-of-the-universe-has-a-map-and-a-name\/","fs_url_headline":"For the first time, our region of the universe has a map and a name","fs_caption":null,"fs_byline":null,"fs_credit":null,"fs_description":null,"fs_body":"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=rENyyRwxpHo"},"knowmore":{"meta_link":"http:\/\/www.washingtonpost.com\/news\/speaking-of-science\/wp\/2014\/09\/03\/for-the-first-time-our-region-of-the-universe-has-a-map-and-a-name\/","meta_title":"For the first time, our region of the universe has a map and a name"},"children":[],"video":{"host":"www.youtube.com","id":"rENyyRwxpHo","embed":"<iframe id=\"ytplayer\" type=\"text\/html\" width=\"960\" height=\"720\" src=\"http:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/rENyyRwxpHo?autoplay=0&enablejsapi=1&wmode=transparent\" frameborder=\"0\"><\/iframe>","thumbnail":"http:\/\/img.youtube.com\/vi\/rENyyRwxpHo\/0.jpg"}},{"id":5416,"title":"The cities where rent, utilities and furniture are most expensive","content":"<p>This chart shows the amount of money people in several major cities spend annually on housing and related expenses, according to <a href=\"http:\/\/www.bls.gov\/spotlight\/2014\/housing\/pdf\/housing.pdf\">a new report<\/a> from the Bureau of Labor Statistics. It includes things like rent, mortgages, heating oil and cleaning agents -- not food, gasoline or medical care, which are also important items on every household's budget, of course. Although Washington, D.C. is at the top of this chart, it's important to keep in mind that the median income in the capital is higher than in other large cities. Even taking Washington's high cost of living into account, it's still one of <a href=\"http:\/\/www.npr.org\/blogs\/money\/2014\/05\/20\/313131559\/how-far-your-paycheck-goes-in-356-u-s-cities\">the wealthiest towns in the country<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>A tip of the hat to <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/lydiadepillis\/status\/508990254171160576\">Lydia DePillis<\/a>.<\/p>\n","author":"Max Ehrenfreund","date":"September 8 at 3:35 pm","link":"http:\/\/knowmore.washingtonpost.com\/2014\/09\/08\/the-cities-where-rent-utilities-and-furniture-are-most-expensive\/","format":"image","info":{"fs_type":"image","fs_uuid":null,"fs_url":"http:\/\/www.npr.org\/blogs\/money\/2014\/05\/20\/313131559\/how-far-your-paycheck-goes-in-356-u-s-cities","fs_url_headline":"How far your paycheck goes in 356 U.S. cities","fs_caption":null,"fs_byline":null,"fs_credit":null,"fs_description":null,"fs_body":""},"knowmore":{"meta_link":"http:\/\/www.npr.org\/blogs\/money\/2014\/05\/20\/313131559\/how-far-your-paycheck-goes-in-356-u-s-cities","meta_title":"How far your paycheck goes in 356 U.S. cities"},"children":[{"ID":5418,"post_author":"587","post_date":"2014-09-08 15:22:25","post_date_gmt":"2014-09-08 19:22:25","post_content":"Bureau of Labor Statistics","post_title":"Expensive cities","post_excerpt":"","post_status":"inherit","comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","post_password":"","post_name":"expensive-cities","to_ping":"","pinged":"","post_modified":"2014-09-08 15:22:25","post_modified